└── media/                 # Sample screenshots or test video clips
```

## ▶️ Usage

Run the main detector:

```bash
python ball_detector.py
```

Or retrain the model (if you’ve updated the dataset):

```bash
python train_model.py
```

## 🔬 Training Data

To retrain, place your labeled images in:

```
dataset/
├── ball/         # Positive samples (images with golf balls)
└── background/   # Negative samples (no golf balls)
```

